sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server

    Note over Client,Server: HTTP/3 runs over QUIC (UDP port 443)

    Note over Client,Server: New connection: 1 RTT
    Client->>Server: QUIC Initial + TLS ClientHello\n(UDP datagram)
    Server-->>Client: QUIC Initial + ServerHello\nHandshake + Certificate + Finished

    Note over Client: Verify certificate
    Client->>Server: QUIC Handshake Finished\n+ HTTP/3 SETTINGS frame

    Note over Client,Server: Application data begins — streams are independent
    Client->>Server: HEADERS frame stream 0\nGET /index.html
    Client->>Server: HEADERS frame stream 4\nGET /api/data
    Server-->>Client: HEADERS + DATA stream 0\n200 OK + HTML
    Server-->>Client: HEADERS + DATA stream 4\n200 OK + JSON

    Note over Client,Server: Packet loss only affects owning stream
    Note over Client,Server: Connection migration: client changes IP
    Client->>Server: PATH_CHALLENGE (new IP address)
    Server-->>Client: PATH_RESPONSE (connection continues)

    Note over Client,Server: 0-RTT resumption on next visit
    Client->>Server: 0-RTT data + Early data HTTP request
    Server-->>Client: 1-RTT response
